item.title: CVE-2016-9986|2024-08-06T03:07:31.824Z -- ibm -- jazz%20reporting%20service
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation Reporting Service (JRS) 5.0 and 6.0 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 120552.
